---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
    description: "Learn more about Sathira Kulathunga and this blog",
    title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
    <h1 class="title mb-12">About</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
        <p>
            Hi, I'm Sathira Kulathunga, a software engineer who loves building things and exploring new technologies.
            This is my personal space on the internet where I share my journey in tech, from homelab experiments
            to DevOps adventures.
        </p>
        <p>What you'll find here:</p>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
            <li>Stories about software engineering and development</li>
            <li>Homelab and infrastructure experiments</li>
            <li>DevOps, Kubernetes, and cloud technologies</li>
            <li>Linux, system administration, and tooling</li>
            <li>Thoughts on technology and the developer experience</li>
            <li>Projects I'm working on and things I'm learning</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            Feel free to explore the blog posts and notes. If you'd like to connect or have any questions,
            you can find me on the social links below.
        </p>
    </div>
</PageLayout>
